{
  "id": "adv_event_2404_01_01",
  "title": "ⅢXの\n世界進出",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃじゃーん！！\nkanaから二人に、大事なお知らせがありま～す！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ta-da!!\nkana have a very important announcement for the two of you~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8999999643,
      "endTime": 8.8512016893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……一体なんなの、藪から棒に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What is it all of a sudden?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.064535137,
      "endTime": 11.8782227476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "kanaの世界進出が決定しました～！　きゃはっ！\nちゃんとⅢXの宣伝もしてくるから安心して待ってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been decided that kana is going global~! Kyaha!\nI'll properly promote IIIX too‚ so don't worry and wait for me‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.0848893762,
      "endTime": 21.6463630319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "姫野のせいでBIG4落ちして、今はこんな零細事務所\nにいるけどさ。いつまでも、ここに居たい訳じゃないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because of Himeno‚ we got kicked out of BIG4‚ and now we're stuck\nin this tiny agency‚ but… It's not like I want to stay here forever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8596960982,
      "endTime": 29.9757504424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "パーっと人気を回復させて、世界中にⅢXの……\nいや、kanaの名を轟かせてやるわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll make a huge comeback and let the whole world know about IIIX…\nNo‚ I'll make sure everyone knows kana's name!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1757504424,
      "endTime": 38.5052971801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……勝手にどうぞ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… Suit yourself~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7052972755,
      "endTime": 42.3300817928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "は？　何その反応",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What's with that reaction?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.5167483927,
      "endTime": 45.567020428300005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、まぁ物足りないのは確かよね\n次のライブも箱はしょぼいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'll admit it is a little unsatisfying.\nOur next live venue is shabby‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7803537568,
      "endTime": 51.387678166200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "一瞬で人気が爆発するような、インパクトのある手段が\nあるなら、みんなやってるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If there was some impactful method that could make us\ninstantly popular‚ everyone would be doing it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5943448902,
      "endTime": 57.3965950848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "いっそ、お笑いコンテストにでも出てみる？\n別の客層にアピール出来るかもしれないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why don't we try going on a comedy contest?\nWe might be able to appeal to a different audience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6032617133,
      "endTime": 63.4571619553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "この冷えっ冷えの仲の私達で漫才を？\n客席が盛り下がるだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doing manzai with our ice-cold relationship?\nThe audience's mood would just drop.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.6638285837,
      "endTime": 69.22928669070001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "そこ、話聞けよ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ listen to me!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4426199478,
      "endTime": 71.9491929096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "実はさぁ、ちょっと前にkanaが投稿した動画が\n海外で凄いバズったんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You see‚ the video that kana posted a while back\nwent super viral overseas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1891893586,
      "endTime": 78.91363403390001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "海外の有名アーティストにも拡散されて\n英語のコメントも殺到してさぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was shared by famous overseas artists‚\nand there was a ton of English comments.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1069674055,
      "endTime": 85.5577156583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "その話は知ってるわよ\nこの一ヶ月、どれだけ聞かされたと思ってるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know about that.\nHow many times do you think I've heard about it this past month?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7443823059,
      "endTime": 91.533860894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "で、動画を観たアメリカのプロモーターから\n『ラスベガスでショーに出ないか』って連絡がきたの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ an American promoter saw the video and\ncontacted me‚ asking‚ 'Would you like to perform in a show in Las Vegas?'!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7271940748,
      "endTime": 99.785788111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "ラスベガス？\nカジノの街に、なんでkanaが呼ばれるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Las Vegas?\nWhy would they invite kana to a casino city?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9857879202,
      "endTime": 105.0567253629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ラスベガスは、カジノが有名だけど\nホテルとかカジノで、ショーもしょちゅうやってるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Las Vegas is famous for its casinos‚\nbut it also frequently hosts shows in hotels and casinos.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2433920582,
      "endTime": 111.3362263402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "サーカスの劇場とか、eスポーツの大会なんかもあるし\n世界でも指折りの、エンタテインメントの街って訳",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It also has circus theaters and esports tournaments‚\nso it's basically one of the world's leading entertainment cities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5362264355,
      "endTime": 120.5117597302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "詳しいのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem well-informed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7184262634,
      "endTime": 122.0639318467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。franの言った通りkanaが\n世界レベルのエンターテイナーだから呼ばれたってこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep‚ yep. Just like fran said‚ that's why\nthey called me because kana is a world-class entertainer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3972631574,
      "endTime": 129.9517530562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "ま、そんな訳でラスベガス行ってくるから\nkanaがいなくて寂しいと思うけど留守番よろしくね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I'm going to Las Vegas.\nWatch the house while I'm gone‚ okay? You must be sad without me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.1517528654,
      "endTime": 138.3296892286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "そーだ！　あんた達には先にサインあげようか？\nあ、今ならお土産のリクエストも聞いてあげる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right! Should I give you my autograph first?\nI'm even taking requests for souvenirs now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5363560479,
      "endTime": 146.868577842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "……嘘でしょ\nこの子が、私達にもお土産買ってくるとか言うなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It can't be.\nThis girl is saying she'll buy souvenirs for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.0752446612,
      "endTime": 152.46179775800002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "まず突っ込むところがそこなの？\n……まぁ実際、明日は雪でも降りそうだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that the first thing you point out?\n…Well‚ actually‚ pigs might fly tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.6617979487,
      "endTime": 159.7624227961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "え～何～聞こえないなぁ～？　ひがみですか～？\n今日のkanaはそんな安い挑発乗らないけどね～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~ What~? I can't hear you? Are you jealous?\nToday's kana won't fall for such cheap provocations~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.9624227007,
      "endTime": 171.26242270080002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ラスベガス近郊　空港",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Airport near Las Vegas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.2557559769,
      "endTime": 173.5690842908,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1811.0121925000158
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.5690842908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_01-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "来た来た来た、ラスベガスーーー！！\nここからkanaの世界的アイドルへの道が始まる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm here‚ I'm here‚ I'm here‚ Las Vegas---!!\nFrom here‚ kana's path to become a global idol begins…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.4890852412,
      "endTime": 183.655752035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
